**Town Crier** | Townsfolk Miscellaneous
__Basics__
The Town Crier knows another townsfolks's role at the start of the game.
__Details__
The Town Crier will be told the role and identity of one other arbitrary person from the Townsfolk team at the start of the game. This information is one-directional.
The role given is not under the influence of any other powers, and therefore is completely reliable. 

__Simplified__
The Town Crier knows another townsfolks's role and identity at the start of the game.
